-611f-5377-892f-9465baf3c023"], "batch": ["au_julian_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1885", "description": ["Daily New ser. v. 21, no. 24 (Aug. 16, 1885)-new ser. v. 35, no. 323 (July 19, 1900) ; v. 71, no. 168 (July 20, 1900)-155th year, no. 47 (Nov. 21, 1982). On Saturday published as: Saturday morning, Apr. 2, 1977-Apr. 1, 1978; The Montgomery advertiser/Alabama journal, Apr. 8, 1978-Nov. 20, 1982. On Sunday published as: Montgomery advertiser and Alabama journal, Dec. 1, 1940-Nov. 21, 1982. Publisher varies: Advertiser Co., <1887> Numbering is irregular. Issues for Aug 16, 1885-July 19, 1899 called also Old ser. v. 54-v. 68. Also issued on microfilm from the University of Alabama Library, and the Library of Congress, Photoduplication Services. Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Weekly eds.: Montgomery weekly advertiser, and: Weekly advertiser (Montgomery, Ala.), and: Montgomery advertiser (Montgomery, Ala. : Weekly). Advertiser (Montgomery, Ala.) 0745-3221 (DLC)sn 82008412 (OCoLC)9049482"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:11.942Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-14", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-14"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn84020645/", "image_url": [], "index": 11, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [32.376542, -86.2996608], "location": ["montgomery", "montgomery county", "united states", "alabama"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-86.2996608, 32.376542], "number": ["2993-9143", "kansas state hist soc, newsp proj", "center for research libraries", "sn86050479", "9739", "panhandle-plains hist mus", "sn84020645", "center for res libr, newsp proj", "1", "2685433", "sn84023549", "univ of kentucky libr", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn84020645/1901-05-01/ed-1/", "wisconsin hist soc, newsp proj", "2024-05-25t20:25:50.256555", "microfilm master", "virginia histo